Insider Activity


Individual




Lawrence A. Hilsheimer



Mr. Lawrence A. Hilsheimer is Chief Financial Officer & Executive Vice President at Greif, Inc., Independent Non-Executive Director at Installed Building Products, Inc., Executive Vice President at Nationwide Financial Services, Inc., Treasurer at Nationwide Children's Hospital, and Executive Vice President-Finance at Crestbrook Insurance Co. He is on the Board of Directors at Installed Building Products, Inc., The Ohio State University, Ohio State University Alumni Association, Inc., and Battelle for Kids.
Mr. Hilsheimer was previously employed as Chief Financial Officer & Executive Vice President by Scotts Miracle-Gro Co., Partner by Deloitte & Touche USA LLP, and President-Nationwide Direct & Customer Solutions by Nationwide Mutual Insurance Co. He also served on the board at Nationwide Life Insurance Co.
He received his undergraduate degree from the Fisher College of Business and a graduate degree from Capital University Law School.



